nodes.text: "Una Duey Dee" was a song performed by Kra Mer 5. DJ R-3X played the song at Oga's Cantina in Black Spire Outpost on the planet Batuu.

"Una Duey Dee" is a song written and recorded for the theme park land Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge, where it plays inside Oga's Cantina. According to the 2001 Star Wars Legends book Galactic Phrase Book & Travel Guide, the words "una duey dee" were Gungan Basic for "one two three."
